<div class="auth-card" style="max-width:680px"><h1 class="h3">Install Rock Bluffs Portal</h1><p class="text-muted">The installer creates the database structure, writes the environment file, and creates the first administrator.</p><form method="post" action="/install"><?=csrf_field()?><h2 class="h6 mt-4">Application</h2><input class="form-control mb-2" name="app_url" placeholder="https://services.rockbluffs.com" required><h2 class="h6 mt-4">MySQL</h2><div class="row g-2"><div class="col"><input class="form-control" name="db_host" value="127.0.0.1" required></div><div class="col"><input class="form-control" name="db_database" value="rockbluffs_exterior" required></div></div><div class="row g-2 mt-1"><div class="col"><input class="form-control" name="db_username" placeholder="Database user" required></div><div class="col"><input class="form-control" type="password" name="db_password" placeholder="Database password" required></div></div><h2 class="h6 mt-4">Administrator</h2><input class="form-control mb-2" name="admin_name" placeholder="Name" required><input class="form-control mb-2" type="email" name="admin_email" placeholder="Email" required><input class="form-control mb-2" type="password" minlength="12" name="admin_password" placeholder="Password" required><button class="btn btn-primary mt-3 w-100">Install portal</button></form></div>
